01:26:07.228 --> 01:26:08.868
Let's hope
the doc made contact.

01:26:14.668 --> 01:26:16.001
Go. Go.

01:26:25.945 --> 01:26:27.814
What are you doing?

01:26:27.815 --> 01:26:30.984
All the cameras are connected.
